defaultBackground.
defaultThis submission is based on Llandovery, Carmarthenshire, to highlight the public transport problems in this rural area. 
defaultThe main form of transport, as in all rural areas, being the private car.
defaultTransport is needed for employment, further educa
defaulttion, hospital visits, entertainment and shopping.
defaultThe main problems are lack of transport combined with the lack of co-ordination between modes of transport resulting in difficulties
default for both able and disabled members of the community.
default&#xa0;
